  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Sales Executive",
  "description": "<h2><strong>Role Overview</strong></h2><p>As a Sales Executive, you will be the driving force behind our market expansion. You are responsible for the full sales lifecycle from cold-calling and prospecting to securing high-level meetings and performing on-site project assessments.</p><h2><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h2><ul><li><p><strong>Lead Generation & Prospecting:</strong> Proactively identify and engage potential B2B and B2C clients through cold-calling, email marketing, and social selling.</p></li><li><p><strong>Relationship Management:</strong> Secure and lead meetings with key decision-makers to pitch business opportunities and negotiate contracts.</p></li><li><p><strong>Market Strategy:</strong> Collaborate directly with the Sales Lead/Manager to analyze market trends and develop winning sales proposals.</p></li><li><p><strong>Outdoor Sales & Networking:</strong> Represent the company at industry events and networking functions to expand our brand footprint.</p></li><li><p><strong>Operational Excellence:</strong> Manage daily administrative tasks and maintain accurate records of leads and follow-ups.</p></li><li><p><strong>Goal Alignment:</strong> Meet and exceed both individual KPIs and departmental sales targets.</p></li></ul><h2><strong>Requirements</strong></h2><ul><li><p><strong>Education:</strong> Diploma, Advanced/Higher/Graduate Diploma in Business Studies or a related field.</p></li><li><p><strong>Experience:</strong> At least <strong>2 years</strong> of proven experience in outdoor sales or business development.</p></li><li><p><strong>Core Skills:</strong> Strong negotiation, persuasion, and closing skills are essential.</p></li><li><p><strong>Adaptability:</strong> Ability to work independently in a fast-paced environment while contributing to team success.</p></li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Urgently Hiring.</strong></p>",
  "minimumYearsExperience": 2,
